name: 163400cb1130412f8f9d4569bc4b58e8@2x (reprocess series)
description: I reflect to the frying lens, I stack and recompose, my mind is a bucket of everything I've seen. I'm lost at the sight of it. I pour it down to pixels. Pixels stare back at me pushed by the aliveness of those who experience them. Gosh. We are all in these gaps between atoms floating and nothing feels that solid. I am a part of you as you are a part of me. Here, have a piece of memory that has dangled from one of my thoughtforms. It glimmers in the mainframe assisted by the motherboard, electric
